articles.author: Alex  Stambaugh, Anna Cooban
articles.title: Ukraine ends supply of Russian gas to Europe - CNN
articles.description: Ukraine has made good on its promise to halt the transport of Russian gas to Europe through its territory after a key deal with Moscow expired on Wednesday.
